title: And CeeLo Green Wore...Exactly What To The Grammys?
text:
And CeeLo Green Wore...Exactly What To The Grammys? Essence 8 hrs ago Paula Rogo Â© getty images
What is CeeLo Green wearing?
That was the question on everyone's mind as the Forget You singer made his way down the 2017 Grammys red carpet Sunday night.
And here we have who we assume is @CeeLoGreen . ðŸ™ƒ #GRAMMYs pic.twitter.com/GYhwrwZFBr

Why is CeeLo Green dressed like a Ferrero Rocher ðŸ˜‚ðŸ’€ #GRAMMYs pic.twitter.com/Cx63rr77Qg

Well, ok!
